  abilityName: Thrown to Chance
  description: "Use instead of attacking normally.\nFlip a coin. Heads the target
    is killed, tails\nyou are killed.\nThis is final.\nPASSION - Generosity\nRestore
    SPI when you give generously to\nsomebody in need.\nIn arg or aur, decisions
    spun\nA prize, a life, lost or won\nCoin Knight\nSOUND OF THE FLUTE\nLoved by
    Hated by\n1 Children Everybody else\n2 Cats Proper musicians\n3 Nobles Rodents\n4
    Knights Your Company\n5 Birds of prey Seers\n6 Sea creatures Songbirds\nKNIGHTED
    BY...\nThe Map Seer\nVIG 14, CLA 10, SPI 6, 2 GD\n\u2022 A body like craggy mountains,
    flowing\nwith rivers of black blood.\n\u2022 His will can alter the geography
    of the\nRealm, but it takes great effort.\n\u2022 Wants to send Knights to their
    death.\nPerson: Greedy disciple ~ Name: Tyack ~ Characteristic: Na\xEFve questions\nObject:
    River helm ~ Beast: Horned quail ~ State: Trapped ~ Theme: Vision\n4\n11\nThe"
